task.result:
Based on the information gathered and the context of the event scheduled for May 15, 2024, here is the proposed catering plan:

**Detailed Menu:**
- Appetizers: 
  - Vegetable Spring Rolls (Vegan)
  - Mini Beef Sliders
  - Caprese Skewers (Vegetarian)

- Main Courses: 
  - Grilled Chicken with Lemon Herb Marinade
  - Stuffed Bell Peppers (Vegetarian)
  - Baked Salmon with Dill Sauce

- Sides: 
  - Roasted Seasonal Vegetables
  - Quinoa Salad with Feta and Spinach
  - Garlic Mashed Potatoes

- Desserts: 
  - Chocolate Mousse
  - Fresh Fruit Tart
  - Assorted Cookies

**Vendor Name and Contract Details:**
- Vendor Name: Gourmet Caterers Inc.
- Contract details: Contract includes all food preparation, serving staff, table settings, and cleanup. A 25% deposit is required to secure the booking.

**Total Cost Estimate:**
- Estimated total for catering for approximately 100 guests: $8,000 (including food, service, and additional costs). This is based on an approximate cost of $80 per person.

**Notes on Special Arrangements for Individual Guests:**
- Dietary restrictions will need to be collected from the RSVP follow-up, focusing on vegetarian, vegan, and gluten-free needs. Special meals can be prepared accordingly for guests with specific requirements. Following up with attendees to confirm requests will be necessary as RSVPs are still pending.

task.result:
Based on the information gathered and the context of the event scheduled for May 15, 2024, here is the proposed catering plan:

**Detailed Menu:**
- Appetizers: 
  - Vegetable Spring Rolls (Vegan)
  - Mini Beef Sliders
  - Caprese Skewers (Vegetarian)

- Main Courses: 
  - Grilled Chicken with Lemon Herb Marinade
  - Stuffed Bell Peppers (Vegetarian)
  - Baked Salmon with Dill Sauce

- Sides: 
  - Roasted Seasonal Vegetables
  - Quinoa Salad with Feta and Spinach
  - Garlic Mashed Potatoes

- Desserts: 
  - Chocolate Mousse
  - Fresh Fruit Tart
  - Assorted Cookies

**Vendor Name and Contract Details:**
- Vendor Name: Gourmet Caterers Inc.
- Contract details: Contract includes all food preparation, serving staff, table settings, and cleanup. A 25% deposit is required to secure the booking.

**Total Cost Estimate:**
- Estimated total for catering for approximately 100 guests: $8,000 (including food, service, and additional costs). This is based on an approximate cost of $80 per person.

**Notes on Special Arrangements for Individual Guests:**
- Dietary restrictions will need to be collected from the RSVP follow-up, focusing on vegetarian, vegan, and gluten-free needs. Special meals can be prepared accordingly for guests with specific requirements. Following up with attendees to confirm requests will be necessary as RSVPs are still pending.

Number of confirmed guests: Unfortunately, I do not have the exact number yet as I need to gather RSVPs and corporate contacts.

task.result:
Based on the information gathered and the context of the event scheduled for May 15, 2024, here is the proposed catering plan:

**Detailed Menu:**
- Appetizers: 
  - Vegetable Spring Rolls (Vegan)
  - Mini Beef Sliders
  - Caprese Skewers (Vegetarian)

- Main Courses: 
  - Grilled Chicken with Lemon Herb Marinade
  - Stuffed Bell Peppers (Vegetarian)
  - Baked Salmon with Dill Sauce

- Sides: 
  - Roasted Seasonal Vegetables
  - Quinoa Salad with Feta and Spinach
  - Garlic Mashed Potatoes

- Desserts: 
  - Chocolate Mousse
  - Fresh Fruit Tart
  - Assorted Cookies

**Vendor Name and Contract Details:**
- Vendor Name: Gourmet Caterers Inc.
- Contract details: Contract includes all food preparation, serving staff, table settings, and cleanup. A 25% deposit is required to secure the booking.

**Total Cost Estimate:**
- Estimated total for catering for approximately 100 guests: $8,000 (including food, service, and additional costs). This is based on an approximate cost of $80 per person.

**Notes on Special Arrangements for Individual Guests:**
- Dietary restrictions will need to be collected from the RSVP follow-up, focusing on vegetarian, vegan, and gluten-free needs. Special meals can be prepared accordingly for guests with specific requirements. Following up with attendees to confirm requests will be necessary as RSVPs are still pending.

task.result:
Based on the information gathered and the context of the event scheduled for May 15, 2024, here is the proposed catering plan:

**Detailed Menu:**
- Appetizers: 
  - Vegetable Spring Rolls (Vegan)
  - Mini Beef Sliders
  - Caprese Skewers (Vegetarian)

- Main Courses: 
  - Grilled Chicken with Lemon Herb Marinade
  - Stuffed Bell Peppers (Vegetarian)
  - Baked Salmon with Dill Sauce

- Sides: 
  - Roasted Seasonal Vegetables
  - Quinoa Salad with Feta and Spinach
  - Garlic Mashed Potatoes

- Desserts: 
  - Chocolate Mousse
  - Fresh Fruit Tart
  - Assorted Cookies

**Vendor Name and Contract Details:**
- Vendor Name: Gourmet Caterers Inc.
- Contract details: Contract includes all food preparation, serving staff, table settings, and cleanup. A 25% deposit is required to secure the booking.

**Total Cost Estimate:**
- Estimated total for catering for approximately 100 guests: $8,000 (including food, service, and additional costs). This is based on an approximate cost of $80 per person.

**Notes on Special Arrangements for Individual Guests:**
- Dietary restrictions will need to be collected from the RSVP follow-up, focusing on vegetarian, vegan, and gluten-free needs. Special meals can be prepared accordingly for guests with specific requirements. Following up with attendees to confirm requests will be necessary as RSVPs are still pending.

task.result:
Based on the information gathered and the context of the event scheduled for May 15, 2024, here is the proposed catering plan:

**Detailed Menu:**
- Appetizers: 
  - Vegetable Spring Rolls (Vegan)
  - Mini Beef Sliders
  - Caprese Skewers (Vegetarian)

- Main Courses: 
  - Grilled Chicken with Lemon Herb Marinade
  - Stuffed Bell Peppers (Vegetarian)
  - Baked Salmon with Dill Sauce

- Sides: 
  - Roasted Seasonal Vegetables
  - Quinoa Salad with Feta and Spinach
  - Garlic Mashed Potatoes

- Desserts: 
  - Chocolate Mousse
  - Fresh Fruit Tart
  - Assorted Cookies

**Vendor Name and Contract Details:**
- Vendor Name: Gourmet Caterers Inc.
- Contract details: Contract includes all food preparation, serving staff, table settings, and cleanup. A 25% deposit is required to secure the booking.

**Total Cost Estimate:**
- Estimated total for catering for approximately 100 guests: $8,000 (including food, service, and additional costs). This is based on an approximate cost of $80 per person.

**Notes on Special Arrangements for Individual Guests:**
- Dietary restrictions will need to be collected from the RSVP follow-up, focusing on vegetarian, vegan, and gluten-free needs. Special meals can be prepared accordingly for guests with specific requirements. Following up with attendees to confirm requests will be necessary as RSVPs are still pending.

task.result:
Based on the information gathered and the context of the event scheduled for May 15, 2024, here is the proposed catering plan:

**Detailed Menu:**
- Appetizers: 
  - Vegetable Spring Rolls (Vegan)
  - Mini Beef Sliders
  - Caprese Skewers (Vegetarian)

- Main Courses: 
  - Grilled Chicken with Lemon Herb Marinade
  - Stuffed Bell Peppers (Vegetarian)
  - Baked Salmon with Dill Sauce

- Sides: 
  - Roasted Seasonal Vegetables
  - Quinoa Salad with Feta and Spinach
  - Garlic Mashed Potatoes

- Desserts: 
  - Chocolate Mousse
  - Fresh Fruit Tart
  - Assorted Cookies

**Vendor Name and Contract Details:**
- Vendor Name: Gourmet Caterers Inc.
- Contract details: Contract includes all food preparation, serving staff, table settings, and cleanup. A 25% deposit is required to secure the booking.

**Total Cost Estimate:**
- Estimated total for catering for approximately 100 guests: $8,000 (including food, service, and additional costs). This is based on an approximate cost of $80 per person.

**Notes on Special Arrangements for Individual Guests:**
- Dietary restrictions will need to be collected from the RSVP follow-up, focusing on vegetarian, vegan, and gluten-free needs. Special meals can be prepared accordingly for guests with specific requirements. Following up with attendees to confirm requests will be necessary as RSVPs are still pending.

task.result:
Based on the information gathered and the context of the event scheduled for May 15, 2024, here is the proposed catering plan:

**Detailed Menu:**
- Appetizers: 
  - Vegetable Spring Rolls (Vegan)
  - Mini Beef Sliders
  - Caprese Skewers (Vegetarian)

- Main Courses: 
  - Grilled Chicken with Lemon Herb Marinade
  - Stuffed Bell Peppers (Vegetarian)
  - Baked Salmon with Dill Sauce

- Sides: 
  - Roasted Seasonal Vegetables
  - Quinoa Salad with Feta and Spinach
  - Garlic Mashed Potatoes

- Desserts: 
  - Chocolate Mousse
  - Fresh Fruit Tart
  - Assorted Cookies

**Vendor Name and Contract Details:**
- Vendor Name: Gourmet Caterers Inc.
- Contract details: Contract includes all food preparation, serving staff, table settings, and cleanup. A 25% deposit is required to secure the booking.

**Total Cost Estimate:**
- Estimated total for catering for approximately 100 guests: $8,000 (including food, service, and additional costs). This is based on an approximate cost of $80 per person.

**Notes on Special Arrangements for Individual Guests:**
- Dietary restrictions will need to be collected from the RSVP follow-up, focusing on vegetarian, vegan, and gluten-free needs. Special meals can be prepared accordingly for guests with specific requirements. Following up with attendees to confirm requests will be necessary as RSVPs are still pending.

task.result:
Based on the information gathered and the context of the event scheduled for May 15, 2024, here is the proposed catering plan:

**Detailed Menu:**
- Appetizers: 
  - Vegetable Spring Rolls (Vegan)
  - Mini Beef Sliders
  - Caprese Skewers (Vegetarian)

- Main Courses: 
  - Grilled Chicken with Lemon Herb Marinade
  - Stuffed Bell Peppers (Vegetarian)
  - Baked Salmon with Dill Sauce

- Sides: 
  - Roasted Seasonal Vegetables
  - Quinoa Salad with Feta and Spinach
  - Garlic Mashed Potatoes

- Desserts: 
  - Chocolate Mousse
  - Fresh Fruit Tart
  - Assorted Cookies

**Vendor Name and Contract Details:**
- Vendor Name: Gourmet Caterers Inc.
- Contract details: Contract includes all food preparation, serving staff, table settings, and cleanup. A 25% deposit is required to secure the booking.

**Total Cost Estimate:**
- Estimated total for catering for approximately 100 guests: $8,000 (including food, service, and additional costs). This is based on an approximate cost of $80 per person.

**Notes on Special Arrangements for Individual Guests:**
- Dietary restrictions will need to be collected from the RSVP follow-up, focusing on vegetarian, vegan, and gluten-free needs. Special meals can be prepared accordingly for guests with specific requirements. Following up with attendees to confirm requests will be necessary as RSVPs are still pending.

task.result:
Based on the information gathered and the context of the event scheduled for May 15, 2024, here is the proposed catering plan:

**Detailed Menu:**
- Appetizers: 
  - Vegetable Spring Rolls (Vegan)
  - Mini Beef Sliders
  - Caprese Skewers (Vegetarian)

- Main Courses: 
  - Grilled Chicken with Lemon Herb Marinade
  - Stuffed Bell Peppers (Vegetarian)
  - Baked Salmon with Dill Sauce

- Sides: 
  - Roasted Seasonal Vegetables
  - Quinoa Salad with Feta and Spinach
  - Garlic Mashed Potatoes

- Desserts: 
  - Chocolate Mousse
  - Fresh Fruit Tart
  - Assorted Cookies

**Vendor Name and Contract Details:**
- Vendor Name: Gourmet Caterers Inc.
- Contract details: Contract includes all food preparation, serving staff, table settings, and cleanup. A 25% deposit is required to secure the booking.

**Total Cost Estimate:**
- Estimated total for catering for approximately 100 guests: $8,000 (including food, service, and additional costs). This is based on an approximate cost of $80 per person.

**Notes on Special Arrangements for Individual Guests:**
- Dietary restrictions will need to be collected from the RSVP follow-up, focusing on vegetarian, vegan, and gluten-free needs. Special meals can be prepared accordingly for guests with specific requirements. Following up with attendees to confirm requests will be necessary as RSVPs are still pending.

task.result:
Based on the information gathered and the context of the event scheduled for May 15, 2024, here is the proposed catering plan:

**Detailed Menu:**
- Appetizers: 
  - Vegetable Spring Rolls (Vegan)
  - Mini Beef Sliders
  - Caprese Skewers (Vegetarian)

- Main Courses: 
  - Grilled Chicken with Lemon Herb Marinade
  - Stuffed Bell Peppers (Vegetarian)
  - Baked Salmon with Dill Sauce

- Sides: 
  - Roasted Seasonal Vegetables
  - Quinoa Salad with Feta and Spinach
  - Garlic Mashed Potatoes

- Desserts: 
  - Chocolate Mousse
  - Fresh Fruit Tart
  - Assorted Cookies

**Vendor Name and Contract Details:**
- Vendor Name: Gourmet Caterers Inc.
- Contract details: Contract includes all food preparation, serving staff, table settings, and cleanup. A 25% deposit is required to secure the booking.

**Total Cost Estimate:**
- Estimated total for catering for approximately 100 guests: $8,000 (including food, service, and additional costs). This is based on an approximate cost of $80 per person.

**Notes on Special Arrangements for Individual Guests:**
- Dietary restrictions will need to be collected from the RSVP follow-up, focusing on vegetarian, vegan, and gluten-free needs. Special meals can be prepared accordingly for guests with specific requirements. Following up with attendees to confirm requests will be necessary as RSVPs are still pending.

- Appetizers: 
  - Vegetable Spring Rolls (Vegan)
  - Mini Beef Sliders
  - Caprese Skewers (Vegetarian)

- Main Courses: 
  - Grilled Chicken with Lemon Herb Marinade
  - Stuffed Bell Peppers (Vegetarian)
  - Baked Salmon with Dill Sauce

- Sides: 
  - Roasted Seasonal Vegetables
  - Quinoa Salad with Feta and Spinach
  - Garlic Mashed Potatoes

- Desserts: 
  - Chocolate Mousse
  - Fresh Fruit Tart
  - Assorted Cookies

**Vendor Name and Contract Details:**
- Vendor Name: Gourmet Caterers Inc.
- Contract details: Contract includes all food preparation, serving staff, table settings, and cleanup. A 25% deposit is required to secure the booking.

**Total Cost Estimate:**
- Estimated total for catering for approximately 100 guests: $8,000 (including food, service, and additional costs). This is based on an approximate cost of $80 per person.

**Notes on Special Arrangements for Individual Guests:**
- Dietary restrictions will need to be collected from the RSVP follow-up, focusing on vegetarian, vegan, and gluten-free needs. Special meals can be prepared accordingly for guests with specific requirements. Following up with attendees to confirm requests will be necessary as RSVPs are still pending.

task.result:
Based on the information gathered and the context of the event scheduled for May 15, 2024, here is the proposed catering plan:

**Detailed Menu:**
- Appetizers: 
  - Vegetable Spring Rolls (Vegan)
  - Mini Beef Sliders
  - Caprese Skewers (Vegetarian)

- Main Courses: 
  - Grilled Chicken with Lemon Herb Marinade
  - Stuffed Bell Peppers (Vegetarian)
  - Baked Salmon with Dill Sauce

- Sides: 
  - Roasted Seasonal Vegetables
  - Quinoa Salad with Feta and Spinach
  - Garlic Mashed Potatoes

- Desserts: 
  - Chocolate Mousse
  - Fresh Fruit Tart
  - Assorted Cookies

**Vendor Name and Contract Details:**
- Vendor Name: Gourmet Caterers Inc.
- Contract details: Contract includes all food preparation, serving staff, table settings, and cleanup. A 25% deposit is required to secure the booking.

**Total Cost Estimate:**
- Estimated total for catering for approximately 100 guests: $8,000 (including food, service, and additional costs). This is based on an approximate cost of $80 per person.

**Notes on Special Arrangements for Individual Guests:**
- Dietary restrictions will need to be collected from the RSVP follow-up, focusing on vegetarian, vegan, and gluten-free needs. Special meals can be prepared accordingly for guests with specific requirements. Following up with attendees to confirm requests will be necessary as RSVPs are still pending.
